oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Thesaurus Transcriptions: Part 9
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This recording features songs on Hank Snow's album "The Thesaurus Transcriptions." Even though "Blue Yodel No. 12" is listed on the box, it is not in this recording. The song "Barefoot Blues" was not written on the box but has been included on this tape. This is part nine of fifteen tapes for this album. This tape is twenty-three of an unidentified number of tapes.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Hank Snow;
